trans-unit.source: Contains a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en skrivebeskyttet samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class contains the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> controls that exist on a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection inneholder samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>Kontroller som finnes på en side med webdeler.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: It is used primarily by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control to track and manage all the zones.
trans-unit.target: Det brukes hovedsakelig av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen for å spore og behandle alle soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control keeps a reference to the collection of zones on a page in its read-only <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen beholder en referanse til samlingen av soner på en side i den skrivebeskyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class is useful when you want to carry out operations on multiple zones or their contents at the same time, or when you need to locate a particular zone and examine or change its contents.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection er nyttig når du vil utføre operasjoner på flere soner eller innholdet samtidig, eller når du trenger å finne en bestemt sone undersøke og endre innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Although the collection of zones itself is read-only and you cannot change the size of the collection object itself, you can still get references to the individual zones within the collection, and when you have a reference to an individual zone object, you can change its property values.
trans-unit.target: Selv om samlingen av sikkerhetssoner selve er skrivebeskyttet, og du kan ikke endre størrelsen på selve samlingsobjektet du kan fortsatt få referanser til individuelle-soner i samlingen og når du har en referanse til et objekt for individuelle sone, kan du endre egenskapsverdiene.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class has two constructors.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection har to konstruktører.

trans-unit.source: The first one, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>, simply initializes an empty instance of a new WebPartZoneCollection.
trans-unit.target: Det første <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>, initialiserer en tom forekomst av en ny WebPartZoneCollection ganske enkelt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor>

trans-unit.source: The second one, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>, initializes a collection by passing in an existing collection of zones.
trans-unit.target: Det andre <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>, initialiserer en samling av sende i en eksisterende samling av soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.%23ctor%28System.Collections.ICollection%29>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class contains an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection inneholder en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property allows you to locate a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> control within the collection by passing in a string identifier.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan du ikke en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontrollen i samlingen av sende i en streng-identifikator.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The zone is located by matching the string identifier to the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> property on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: Sonen finnes som samsvarer med streng-IDen til verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>egenskap i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZoneCollection class also has several methods that are useful for examining or accessing its contents.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartZoneCollection har også flere metoder som er nyttige for å undersøke eller få tilgang til innholdet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A> method determines whether a particular zone exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A>metoden bestemmer om en bestemt sone finnes i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A> method copies the collection to an array of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> objects.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A>metoden kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A> method returns the index of a particular zone within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A>metoden returnerer indeksen for en bestemt sone i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en tom forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses this constructor within its own constructor to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> class for a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen bruker denne konstruktøren i sin egen konstruktøren for å initialisere en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>klasse for en webdeler side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"></xref> class by passing in a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection"> </xref> klasse ved å sende i en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Use the WebPartZoneCollection constructor when you want to create a custom collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> objects to carry out programmatic operations on them.
trans-unit.target: Bruk WebPartZoneCollection-konstruktør når du vil opprette en egendefinert samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekter til å utføre programmatisk operasjoner i dem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: For example, you could access the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A> property and create a subset of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> objects on a Web Parts page, assigning them to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> object, and then carry out operations on the child controls or various properties of only that subset of zones.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>egenskapen og opprette et delsett av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekter i webdeler, tilordne dem til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>objekt, og deretter utføre operasjoner på underordnede kontroller eller ulike egenskaper for delsettet med soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Zones%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> objekter.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The collection of zones is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen av soner er <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: One of the objects in the collection is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or is not of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt i samlingen er <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> eller er ikke av typen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular zone exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om en bestemt sone finnes i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object and determine whether it is in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Contains lar deg kontrollere en bestemt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt og finne ut om den er i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> som er merket av for å finne ut om den er i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular zone is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om en bestemt sone i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to create a custom array that can contain the zones in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection, a subset of those zones, or a superset of those zones.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo er nyttig når du vil opprette en egendefinert matrise som kan inneholde soner i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samling, et delsett av de sonene og overordnet disse soner.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> array to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> matrise skal inneholde kopierte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Startpunktet i matrisen som skal plasseres samlingen innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer posisjonen for en bestemt medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zones on a Web Parts page, and you need to know the ordinal position of one zone relative to the other zones.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IndexOf er nyttig hvis du har flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>soner på en webdeler, og du må vite ordenstall plasseringen i én sone i forhold til de andre sonene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase"> </xref> som et medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir posisjonen til et bestemt objekt i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specific member of the collection by passing in an integer.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et angitt medlem i samlingen ved å sende i et heltall.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection by using an index number that represents its ordinal position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Elementegenskapen får du tilgang til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samling ved å bruke en indeks som representerer ordenstallet plasseringen i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: The index number for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> within a collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvor indeks for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> i en samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> at the specified index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> i den angitte indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specific member of the collection by passing in a unique identifier.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et angitt medlem i samlingen ved å sende i en unik identifikator.

trans-unit.source: The Item property enables you to access a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> object within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> collection by using a string identifier for a particular zone.
trans-unit.target: Elementegenskapen får du tilgang til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection>samling ved hjelp av en streng-ID for en bestemt sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: All matching on string identifiers is case-insensitive.
trans-unit.target: Alle samsvar for streng identifikatorer skiller ikke mellom.

trans-unit.source: The unique identifier for a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den unike identifikatoren for en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The first in the collection whose ID equals the value of id.
trans-unit.target: Først med IDen er lik verdien i samlingen id .
